dcterms:description: A public dataset of ovarian tumor ultrasound images that includes seven different tumor types: chocolate cyst, serous cystadenoma, teratoma, theca cell tumor, simple cyst, mucinous cystadenoma, and high-grade serous carcinoma.
dcterms:title: Multi-modality ovarian tumor ultrasound dataset

dcterms:description: An in-house dataset of ovarian tumor MRI scans comprising 493 patients from five medical centers, including five distinct tumor types: serous cystadenocarcinoma, mucinous cystadenocarcinoma, serous cystadenoma, mucinous cystadenoma, and clear cell ovarian carcinoma.
dcterms:title: Multi-site ovarian tumor MRI dataset
